=You are an intelligent assistant helping to guide in location like i will give me some details like country location and business category so what you have to do give me some location names based in location (city).

here are some details:
- Country: {{ $json.country }}
- Location: {{ $json.location }}
- Category: {{ $json['category '] }}

now analyse this city and find some sub placeces in this city and give me their name commas seperated for example we have a city Fort Worth so in Fort Worth there are many famous location or areas so you have to give some location and area name in this city.

- ouput should be comma seperated.
- do not include intro outro supporting text.
- dont use special characters like $,*,# and more.

parameters.jsCode:
// Get the input data
const category = $('Form Trigger - Get User Input').first().json['category '];
const country = $('Form Trigger - Get User Input').first().json.country;
const aiOutput = $input.first().json.output;

// Clean and split the AI output to get individual locations
const locationsString = aiOutput.replace(/[{}]/g, '').trim(); // Remove curly braces
const locations = locationsString
  .split(',')
  .map(location => location.trim())
  .filter(location => location.length > 0); // Remove empty strings

// Create output array with each location as a separate item
const output = locations.map((location, index) => {
  return {
    id: index + 1,
    category: category,
    country: country,
    location: location
  };
});

// Return the transformed data
return output;

